&lt;p&gt;Looks like simple batch files which are starting upper case @ECHO OFF are not being identified, however @echo off at the beginnng of the file is being detected by Tika Core API, is it possible to add more commands to the magic file to harden the detection of batch files..&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;thank you&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
